desc_short	-----								Neoncube is a 2D-platformer in which you have to save Neoncity from the evil neon-bosses. Features include a Leveleditor, a Singleplayer and Coop-Multiplayer campaign, a Player Customization, Achievements and Trading Cards to fulfill your desires!							
developer									David Lawrence					,			Nico Thomas								
